<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Welcome</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" />
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');

      :root {
        --primary-color: #2a3990; /* Dark blue */
        --secondary-color: #4e54c8; /* Purple */
        --accent-color: #ff6b6b; /* Coral red */
        --background-color: #f8f9ff; /* Light background */
        --card-color: #ffffff; /* White */
        --text-color: #333344; /* Dark text */
        --light-text: #7b7b8f; /* Light gray text */
        --shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08); /* Soft shadow */
        --hover-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12); /* Hover shadow */
        --transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1); /* Smooth transition */
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      body {
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: var(--background-color);
        color: var(--text-color);
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        min-height: 100vh;
      }

      /* Welcome Container */
      .welcome-container {
        background-color: var(--card-color);
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        padding: 40px;
        max-width: 800px;
        text-align: center;
        transition: var(--transition);
      }

      .welcome-container:hover {
        box-shadow: var(--hover-shadow);
      }

      .welcome-container h1 {
        font-size: 36px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
      }

      .welcome-container h1::after {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -10px;
        left: 50%;
        transform: translateX(-50%);
        width: 80px;
        height: 3px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
        border-radius: 2px;
      }

      .welcome-message {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .welcome-message p {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--light-text);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }

      .welcome-message p strong {
        color: var(--primary-color);
      }

      .start-button {
        padding: 12px 28px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));
        color: white;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 30px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: 500;
        font-size: 16px;
        transition: var(--transition);
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(42, 57, 144, 0.2);
      }

      .start-button::before {
        content: '';
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2), transparent);
        transition: all 0.6s;
      }

      .start-button:hover {
        transform: translateY(-3px);
        box-shadow: 0 7px 20px rgba(42, 57, 144, 0.3);
      }

      .start-button:hover::before {
        left: 100%;
      }

      /* Responsive Design */
      @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .welcome-container {
          padding: 20px;
        }

        .welcome-container h1 {
          font-size: 28px;
        }

        .welcome-message p {
          font-size: 14px;
        }

        .start-button {
          padding: 10px 20px;
          font-size: 14px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="welcome-container">
      <h1>Welcome, <%= username %>!</h1>

      <div class="welcome-message">
        <p>
          <strong>We're thrilled to have you here!</strong> At CareerPath, we're dedicated to helping you discover
          the perfect career path tailored to your unique skills, interests, and aspirations.
        </p>
        <p>
          To get started, we'll ask you a few quick questions about your qualifications, skills, and interests.
          This will help us provide you with the best recommendations and resources to achieve your career goals.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Why is this important?</strong> By understanding your background and preferences, we can:
        </p>
        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 15px 0;">
          <li>✅ Recommend careers that match your strengths and passions.</li>
          <li>✅ Provide personalized learning resources and certifications.</li>
          <li>✅ Help you track your progress and achieve your goals.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Ready to take the first step toward your dream career? Let's get started!
        </p>
      </div>

      <button class="start-button" onclick="window.location.href='/questions/<%= userId %>'">
        Get Started
      </button>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>